《'''发展受阻'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Arrested Development'''''}}）是{{link-en|Mitchell Hurwitz}}为[[福克斯广播公司|Fox]]创作的一部美国[[電視劇|電視]][[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]。该剧叙述了Bluth一家的故事，由2003年一直播放到2006年，共播出三季。自2003年首播以来，该剧获得6项[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]，1项[[金球奖|金球奖]]<ref name="tv">{{cite web|url=http://www.tv.com/news/three-times-the-arrested-development-5534/|title=Three times the Arrested Development|author=Mahan, Colin|publisher=[[TV.com|TV.com]]|date=2007-03-26|accessdate=2007-07-29|archive-date=2019-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421161717/http://www.tv.com/news/three-times-the-arrested-development-5534/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2007年，被《[[時代_(雜誌)|时代]]》杂志评为有史以来最伟大的100部剧集之一。<ref name="Time 100">{{cite news |url=http://entertainment.time.com/2007/09/06/the-100-best-tv-shows-of-all-time/slide/arrested-development-2/#arrested-development-2 |title=The 100 Best TV Shows of All-''TIME'' |first=James |last=Poniewozik |authorlink=James Poniewozik |work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] |publisher=Time.com |accessdate=2010-03-04 |date=2007-09-06 |archive-date=2014-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010150120/http://entertainment.time.com/2007/09/06/the-100-best-tv-shows-of-all-time/slide/arrested-development-2/#arrested-development-2 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>虽然得到评论界好评，该剧的收视率一直不理想，2006年2月10日播出了一个两小时的大结局。最后结局播出以来关于第四季和改编电影的传闻一直存在。在2011年年底，[[Netflix|Netflix]]公司宣布将独家授权其流媒体视频服务上发布新的剧集。<ref name="netflix revival">{{Cite news |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/11/18/arrested-development-netflix/ |title='Arrested Development' officially back! Revived series coming to Netflix |last=Hibberd |first=James |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2011-11-18 |accessdate=2012-02-29 |archive-date=2012-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212122125/http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/11/18/arrested-development-netflix/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>十集将在同一天发布，并计划于2013年五月发布。<ref name="S4 premiere">{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/08/23/arrested-development-spring-netflix_n_1824588.html|title='Arrested Development' Will Premiere In Spring On Netflix|work=Huffington Post|first=Maureen|last=Ryan|date=2012-08-23|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2012-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120824035915/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/08/23/arrested-development-spring-netflix_n_1824588.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>同名电影仍在筹备当中，主要演员将出演自己的角色。<ref>{{cite news |last=Fernandez |first=Jay A. |first2=Lesley |last2=Goldberg |title=Arrested Development script in works |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2009-10-04 |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/10/05/us-arrested-idUSTRE5940H520091005 |accessdate=2009-11-04 |archive-date=2011-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110201035943/http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/10/05/us-arrested-idUSTRE5940H520091005 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

